 beam-aligned effective channels. When the data-aided channel tracking\nis invalid, angles will be re-estimated at the pilot-aided channel tracking\nstage with an equivalent sparse digital array, where angle ambiguity can be\nresolved based on the previously estimated angles. The simulation results and\nthe derived Cram\\'{e}r-Rao lower bounds verify the effectiveness of our\nsolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Mar 2021 16:10:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 11:18:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-04"}
