f lines whenever possible. Our code is publicly\navailable at https://github.com/EmmanuelSchaan/HaloGen/tree/LIM . In a\ncompanion paper, we use this halo model formalism and code to highlight the\ndegeneracies between cosmology and astrophysics in LIM, and to compare the LIM\nobservables to galaxy detection for a number of surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Mar 2021 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2021 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-29"}
