cted as all dynamic variables, including the local\ncontent splitting ratio, the transmission/computation power allocation, and the\nMEC server selection. Numerical results demonstrate that both proposed\nstrategies perform better than the traditional non-learning schemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 04:44:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 15:29:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Feb 2023 09:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-16"}
