 profitable transaction qualifies as\nMiner ExtractableValue (MEV) and would incentivize MEV-aware miners to fork the\nblockchain. For instance, we find that on Ethereum, a miner with a hash rate of\n10% would fork the blockchain if an MEV opportunity exceeds 4x the block\nreward.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 07:42:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-04"}
