l in order to apply functional methods to the\nmatching. We finally match the model to the SM EFT and present the full\none-loop result including operators up to mass dimension six.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Mar 2021 15:57:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-04"}
